(1, 4, 13, 'E-commerce Platform Development', 'We need a full-featured e-commerce website with product catalog, shopping cart, payment integration (Stripe/PayPal), user accounts, order tracking, and admin dashboard. The platform should support multiple currencies and languages. Requires integration with inventory management system and automated email notifications for order updates.', 1, NULL, NULL, 8500.00, 'ecommerce_requirements.txt', '2026-06-15', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-15 09:30:00', 2),
(2, 5, 15, 'Mobile Fitness Tracking Application', 'Development of a cross-platform mobile app (iOS and Android) for fitness tracking with features including: workout logging, calorie counter, progress analytics, social sharing, community challenges, and integration with wearable devices. App should include push notifications, offline mode, and cloud sync for user data. Design should be modern and intuitive with dark mode support.', 3, NULL, 4, 12000.00, 'fitness_app_specs.txt', '2026-07-30', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-18 14:20:00', 1),
(3, 6, 12, 'Corporate Website Redesign & Modernization', 'Complete redesign of our company website with modern UI/UX principles. Requirements include: responsive design for all devices, SEO optimization, blog integration with CMS, team member portal, client testimonials section, and contact forms with lead management. Must improve page load speed and implement analytics tracking. Current site statistics and branding guidelines will be provided.', 1, NULL, NULL, 6500.00, 'corporate_site_guidelines.txt', '2026-05-20', '2.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-10 11:45:00', 3),
(4, 7, -1, 'Human Resources Management Desktop Application', 'Development of a Windows-based HR management system for managing employee records, attendance tracking, leave requests, payroll integration, performance reviews, and document storage. System should include role-based access control, reporting dashboards, and export functionality. Database design must ensure data security and compliance with labor regulations. User documentation and training materials required.', 2, NULL, 1, 9800.00, 'hr_system_requirements.txt', '2026-08-10', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-28 16:00:00', 2),
(5, 8, 18, 'Online Learning Management System (LMS)', 'Creation of a comprehensive learning platform with course creation tools, student enrollment, video hosting, quiz/assessment features, progress tracking, certificates generation, discussion forums, and instructor analytics. Must support multiple file formats (video, PDF, images). Include email notifications, automated grading, and mobile-responsive design. Budget includes initial content migration from existing platform.', 1, NULL, NULL, 15000.00, 'lms_detailed_specifications.txt', '2026-09-25', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-05 10:15:00', 1),
(6, 24, -1, 'Restaurant Ordering Web Platform', 'We need a complete web platform for our restaurant chain to allow customers to order food online for delivery and pickup. Features should include: dynamic menu management, real-time order status tracking, customer reviews and ratings, loyalty program integration, payment gateway (Stripe/Square), order history, and admin panel for order management. Must be mobile-responsive and support multiple restaurant locations.', 1, NULL, NULL, 11000.00, 'restaurant_platform_specs.txt', '2026-07-10', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-12 13:45:00', 1),
(7, 25, -1, 'Inventory Management System Documentation', 'Comprehensive technical and user documentation for our new inventory management system. Needs to include: system architecture documentation, API reference guide, user manual for different role types (admin, warehouse, manager), troubleshooting guide, and video tutorials. Documentation should be available in both Hungarian and English. Requires professional formatting, diagrams, and screenshots.', 4, 'Technical Documentation Project', NULL, 5500.00, 'inventory_system_overview.txt', '2026-06-01', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-08 10:20:00', 1),
(8, 26, -1, 'Cloud Infrastructure Migration & Setup', 'Migration of our existing on-premises servers to AWS cloud infrastructure. Scope includes: infrastructure assessment, cloud architecture design, database migration, application deployment, security configuration, backup and disaster recovery setup. Need high availability configuration and auto-scaling setup for seasonal traffic spikes. Full documentation and staff training on new cloud environment required.', 4, 'Cloud Migration Project', NULL, 18500.00, 'current_infrastructure_audit.txt', '2026-08-20', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-02 09:00:00', 1),
(9, 27, -1, 'Marketing Website & Blog Platform Redesign', 'Complete redesign of our marketing website with modern aesthetics and improved user engagement. New site should feature: responsive design, integrated blog with SEO optimization, newsletter subscription, testimonials showcase, case studies section, contact forms, and analytics integration. Must include CMS for easy content management by marketing team. Performance optimization for fast loading times critical.', 1, NULL, NULL, 8200.00, 'marketing_site_goals.txt', '2026-06-28', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-14 15:30:00', 1),
(10, 28, -1, 'Mobile App for Project Management', 'Development of a mobile application (iOS and Android) for team project management with features including: project creation and management, task assignment and tracking, team collaboration tools, file attachments, progress reporting, notifications, and offline functionality. Must sync seamlessly with our web-based project management system. Include push notifications and intuitive UI for on-the-go project management.', 3, NULL, 4, 14500.00, 'mobile_pm_requirements.txt', '2026-07-15', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-20 11:15:00', 1),
(11, 44, 94, 'AI-Powered Customer Support Chatbot', 'Development of an intelligent chatbot system with natural language processing capabilities for customer support automation. Must integrate with help desk systems, learn from past interactions, and escalate complex issues to human agents. Features include multi-language support, sentiment analysis, and analytics dashboard. Implementation requires deep ML expertise.', 4, 'AI Chatbot System', NULL, 16000.00, 'chatbot_requirements.txt', '2026-08-10', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-21 10:30:00', 2),
(12, 45, 95, 'Healthcare Patient Portal Web Application', 'Build a HIPAA-compliant patient portal for healthcare providers featuring appointment scheduling, medical records access, prescription management, telemedicine integration, and secure messaging with doctors. System must ensure data security, include multi-factor authentication, and support both web and mobile access with synchronized data.', 1, NULL, NULL, 22000.00, 'healthcare_portal_specs.txt', '2026-09-15', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-19 14:00:00', 1),
(13, 46, 96, 'Supply Chain Visibility Platform', 'Create an enterprise platform for real-time supply chain tracking and management. Features include GPS tracking integration, inventory management, vendor performance analytics, automated alert systems for delays, and predictive analytics for demand forecasting. Dashboard should display KPIs and provide actionable insights for decision makers.', 1, NULL, NULL, 25000.00, 'supply_chain_platform.txt', '2026-10-01', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-18 09:45:00', 2),
(14, 47, 97, 'Educational Video Platform Development', 'Development of a comprehensive video streaming platform for educational content with adaptive bitrate streaming, live class integration, student progress tracking, quiz integration, and certificate generation. Must support HD and 4K video, handle high concurrent viewers, and include creator dashboard for educators.', 1, NULL, NULL, 19500.00, 'edu_video_specs.txt', '2026-09-01', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-22 11:20:00', 1),
(15, 48, 98, 'Real Estate Virtual Tour Platform', 'Build an interactive virtual tour platform for real estate with 360-degree panoramic photos, 3D floor plans, property information integration, and agent booking systems. Include mobile app functionality, lead generation tools, and integration with property management systems. Must be SEO-optimized for search engines.', 1, NULL, NULL, 13000.00, 'realestate_tour_specs.txt', '2026-08-25', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-17 13:15:00', 2),
(16, 49, 99, 'Fintech Mobile Banking Application', 'Develop a cutting-edge mobile banking app with digital wallet, peer-to-peer transfers, bill payments, investment tracking, and fintech API integrations. Security is critical - implement multi-factor authentication, biometric login, and encryption. Must comply with banking regulations and pass security audits.', 3, NULL, 5, 31000.00, 'banking_app_requirements.txt', '2026-10-15', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-16 10:00:00', 2),
(17, 50, 100, 'Social Media Analytics Dashboard', 'Create an advanced analytics platform for monitoring and analyzing social media performance across multiple networks. Features include competitor analysis, audience demographics, engagement metrics, trend prediction, and automated reporting. Build with real-time data processing and support for 50+ social platforms.', 1, NULL, NULL, 17000.00, 'social_analytics_specs.txt', '2026-08-30', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-15 15:30:00', 1),
(18, 51, 101, 'IoT Smart Building Management System', 'Implement a comprehensive IoT platform for building automation including HVAC control, lighting management, security systems, and energy monitoring. System must support thousands of connected devices, provide real-time dashboards, and include predictive maintenance features. Integrate with existing building systems.', 2, NULL, 1, 28000.00, 'iot_building_specs.txt', '2026-09-20', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-14 12:45:00', 1),
(19, 52, 102, 'E-Learning Content Management System', 'Develop a sophisticated LMS with advanced course management, student progress analytics, interactive assessments, and adaptive learning paths. Include instructor tools for content creation, student communication, and performance tracking. Support offline learning and mobile accessibility.', 1, NULL, NULL, 20000.00, 'lms_advanced_specs.txt', '2026-09-10', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-13 08:20:00', 2),
(20, 53, 103, 'Blockchain-Based Supply Chain Verification', 'Create a blockchain solution for supply chain verification and product authentication. Features include immutable record-keeping, smart contracts for automated verification, QR code integration for consumers, and real-time tracking. Must ensure transparency, prevent counterfeiting, and provide audit trails.', 4, 'Blockchain Supply Chain', NULL, 35000.00, 'blockchain_specs.txt', '2026-10-30', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-12 14:10:00', 1),
(21, 54, 104, 'AI-Powered Job Matching Platform', 'Build a recruitment platform using machine learning for intelligent job-candidate matching. Include resume parsing, skill assessment, video interview analysis, and predictive hiring analytics. Provide talent insights and create data-driven recruitment strategies for HR teams.', 1, NULL, NULL, 18500.00, 'recruitment_ai_specs.txt', '2026-08-15', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-11 09:30:00', 2),
(22, 55, 105, 'Augmented Reality Furniture Placement App', 'Develop an AR mobile application allowing users to visualize furniture in their space before purchase. Include 3D model library integration, real-time visualization with device camera, purchase directly from app, and AR-based interior design recommendations.', 3, NULL, 4, 16500.00, 'ar_furniture_specs.txt', '2026-08-20', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-10 11:00:00', 1),
(23, 56, 106, 'Professional Networking Platform', 'Create a LinkedIn-like platform for professional networking with features like profile building, connection management, job listings, content sharing, messaging, and recommendation systems. Include notifications, search functionality, and analytics for Premium users.', 1, NULL, NULL, 24000.00, 'networking_platform_specs.txt', '2026-09-25', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-09 16:45:00', 2),
(24, 57, 107, 'Video Conferencing System Development', 'Build an enterprise video conferencing platform with HD video, screen sharing, recording capabilities, chat integration, virtual backgrounds, and meeting scheduling. Include security features like end-to-end encryption and meeting passwords. Support up to 1000 concurrent participants.', 1, NULL, NULL, 26000.00, 'video_conference_specs.txt', '2026-10-05', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-08 13:20:00', 1),
(25, 58, 108, 'Subscription Management Platform', 'Develop a comprehensive subscription billing system supporting multiple payment methods, automated invoicing, dunning management, usage-based billing, and churn prediction. Include customer portal, revenue analytics, and integration with accounting systems.', 1, NULL, NULL, 15000.00, 'subscription_platform_specs.txt', '2026-08-18', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-07 10:15:00', 2),
(26, 59, 109, 'Geolocation-Based Service Discovery App', 'Create a mobile app for discovering nearby services (restaurants, shops, services) with reviews, ratings, real-time availability, reservation systems, and loyalty programs. Include GPS integration, location-based notifications, and integration with payment gateways.', 3, NULL, 4, 13500.00, 'service_discovery_specs.txt', '2026-08-05', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-06 14:30:00', 1),
(27, 60, 110, 'Fleet Management and Tracking System', 'Develop a fleet management platform with real-time GPS tracking, route optimization, fuel consumption monitoring, maintenance scheduling, and driver behavior analytics. Include mobile app for drivers and web dashboard for fleet managers with reporting capabilities.', 1, NULL, NULL, 21000.00, 'fleet_management_specs.txt', '2026-09-12', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-05 09:00:00', 2),
(28, 61, 111, 'Digital Rights Management Platform', 'Build a DRM solution for content creators protecting digital assets with watermarking, encryption, usage restrictions, and licensing management. Include APIs for third-party integration, analytics dashboard, and enforcement mechanisms for unauthorized access prevention.', 1, NULL, NULL, 19000.00, 'drm_platform_specs.txt', '2026-09-05', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-04 11:45:00', 1),
(29, 62, 112, 'Progressive Web App for Food Delivery', 'Develop a PWA for food delivery with offline functionality, push notifications, real-time order tracking, integrated payments, and restaurant management backend. Must work seamlessly on all devices with minimal data usage for emerging markets.', 1, NULL, NULL, 17000.00, 'food_delivery_pwa_specs.txt', '2026-08-22', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-03 15:25:00', 2),
(30, 63, 113, 'Predictive Maintenance AI System', 'Create an AI system for industrial equipment predictive maintenance using machine learning on IoT sensor data. System should predict failures, recommend maintenance schedules, reduce downtime, and optimize maintenance costs. Include dashboard for maintenance teams and integration with CMMS systems.', 4, 'Predictive Maintenance AI', NULL, 32000.00, 'predictive_maintenance_specs.txt', '2026-10-10', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-02 12:30:00', 2),
(31, 64, -1, 'Multi-Vendor Marketplace Platform', 'Build a comprehensive e-commerce marketplace supporting multiple vendors with separate stores, inventory management, commission systems, dispute resolution, and vendor analytics. Include secure payment processing, quality assurance tools, and customer review systems.', 1, NULL, NULL, 27000.00, 'marketplace_specs.txt', '2026-09-30', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-03-01 14:00:00', 1),
(32, 65, -1, 'Event Management and Ticketing System', 'Develop a full event management platform with ticketing, attendee management, seat selection, QR code verification, and post-event analytics. Include payment processing, email notifications, and integration with venue management systems.', 1, NULL, NULL, 16000.00, 'event_ticketing_specs.txt', '2026-08-28', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-28 10:20:00', 1),
(33, 66, -1, 'Document Management and Workflow System', 'Create an enterprise document management system with version control, workflow automation, approval routing, compliance tracking, and full-text search. Include integration with existing systems, audit trails, and digital signature support.', 1, NULL, NULL, 19500.00, 'document_management_specs.txt', '2026-09-08', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-27 13:45:00', 1),
(34, 67, -1, 'Energy Consumption Optimization Platform', 'Build a platform for analyzing and optimizing energy consumption with real-time monitoring, predictive analytics for peak usage, recommendations for energy savings, and carbon footprint tracking. Include API integrations with smart meters.', 1, NULL, NULL, 15000.00, 'energy_optimization_specs.txt', '2026-08-12', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-26 09:30:00', 1),
(35, 68, -1, 'Mental Health Support Application', 'Develop a mental health and wellness application with meditation guides, therapist directory, appointment scheduling, mood tracking, and crisis support resources. Ensure privacy, HIPAA compliance, and integration with professional mental health services.', 1, NULL, NULL, 18000.00, 'mental_health_app_specs.txt', '2026-09-03', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-25 11:15:00', 1),
(36, 69, -1, 'Inventory Forecasting AI System', 'Create an AI-powered inventory management system that predicts demand, optimizes stock levels, identifies slow-moving items, and suggests reorder points. Use historical data and market trends for accurate forecasting to reduce waste and stockouts.', 1, NULL, NULL, 17500.00, 'inventory_ai_specs.txt', '2026-08-20', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-24 14:50:00', 1),
(37, 70, -1, 'Travel Planning Recommendation Engine', 'Build an intelligent travel planning platform using ML to recommend destinations, accommodations, and activities based on user preferences, budget, and past travel history. Include price comparison, booking integration, and itinerary management.', 1, NULL, NULL, 16500.00, 'travel_engine_specs.txt', '2026-08-25', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-23 10:00:00', 1),
(38, 71, -1, 'Custom API Development Framework', 'Develop reusable API framework and middleware components for rapid API development with built-in security, rate limiting, caching, and monitoring. Create comprehensive documentation and developer portal for third-party integrations.', 4, 'API Framework Project', NULL, 14000.00, 'api_framework_specs.txt', '2026-08-15', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-22 15:30:00', 1),
(39, 72, -1, 'Quality Automation Testing Suite', 'Create a comprehensive automated testing platform with test case management, CI/CD integration, cross-browser testing, performance testing, and detailed reporting. Support multiple programming languages and frameworks with easy integration.', 1, NULL, NULL, 13500.00, 'qa_automation_specs.txt', '2026-08-10', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-21 12:10:00', 1),
(40, 73, -1, 'Data Visualization Analytics Engine', 'Build a powerful data visualization platform supporting multiple chart types, real-time data streaming, drill-down capabilities, custom dashboards, and scheduled report generation. Include data source integration and export functionalities.', 1, NULL, NULL, 15500.00, 'data_viz_specs.txt', '2026-08-18', '1.0.0', NULL, '2026-02-20 09:45:00', 1);
INSERT INTO `order_messages` (`oid`, `uid`, `message`, `created_at`) VALUES
(1, 4, 'Hello, I have some questions about the e-commerce platform requirements. Specifically, what payment gateways do you plan to integrate?', '2026-03-16 10:00:00'),
(1, 13, 'Hi! We can integrate Stripe and PayPal as mentioned in the requirements. Do you have any preference?', '2026-03-16 11:00:00'),
(1, 4, 'Stripe would be great. Also, about the inventory management, how will it sync with our existing system?', '2026-03-16 12:00:00'),
(1, 13, 'We\'ll use APIs to sync with your inventory system. I\'ll need the API documentation from you.', '2026-03-16 13:00:00'),
(1, 4, 'Perfect, I\'ll send that over. When can we schedule a kickoff meeting?', '2026-03-16 14:00:00'),
(1, 13, 'How about next Tuesday at 2 PM?', '2026-03-16 15:00:00'),
(2, 5, 'Hi, I\'m excited about the fitness app project. Do you have experience with wearable integrations?', '2026-03-19 10:00:00'),
(2, 15, 'Yes, I\'ve worked with Fitbit and Apple Health APIs before. What wearables do you want to support?', '2026-03-19 11:00:00'),
(2, 5, 'Primarily Fitbit and Apple Watch. Also, about the UI design, I have some mockups ready.', '2026-03-19 12:00:00'),
(2, 15, 'Great, can you share them? I\'ll review and provide feedback.', '2026-03-19 13:00:00'),
(2, 5, 'Sure, sending now. Let\'s discuss the color scheme.', '2026-03-19 14:00:00'),
(2, 15, 'The mockups look good. I suggest a vibrant color palette for motivation.', '2026-03-19 15:00:00'),
(3, 6, 'Hello, for the website redesign, we need SEO optimization. What tools do you use?', '2026-03-11 10:00:00'),
(3, 12, 'I use Google Analytics and SEMrush for SEO. What are your current SEO goals?', '2026-03-11 11:00:00'),
(3, 6, 'Improve organic traffic by 30%. Also, integrate a blog.', '2026-03-11 12:00:00'),
(3, 12, 'Understood. I\'ll include that in the proposal.', '2026-03-11 13:00:00'),
(3, 6, 'Good. When can you start?', '2026-03-11 14:00:00'),
(3, 12, 'As soon as you approve the wireframes.', '2026-03-11 15:00:00'),
(5, 8, 'Hi, for the LMS project, what video hosting solution do you recommend?', '2026-03-06 10:00:00'),
(5, 18, 'I recommend using AWS S3 with CloudFront for scalable video hosting. It handles high traffic well.', '2026-03-06 11:00:00'),
(5, 8, 'That sounds good. How about quiz integration?', '2026-03-06 12:00:00'),
(5, 18, 'We can integrate quizzes with automated grading. What types of assessments do you need?', '2026-03-06 13:00:00'),
(5, 8, 'Multiple choice and essay questions. Also, progress tracking.', '2026-03-06 14:00:00'),
(5, 18, 'Got it. I\'ll design the system accordingly.', '2026-03-06 15:00:00'),
(11, 44, 'Hello, for the AI chatbot, what NLP technologies will you use?', '2026-03-22 10:00:00'),
(11, 94, 'We\'ll use Google Dialogflow or Microsoft Bot Framework for NLP. Which do you prefer?', '2026-03-22 11:00:00'),
(11, 44, 'Dialogflow is fine. How about multi-language support?', '2026-03-22 12:00:00'),
(11, 94, 'Dialogflow supports multiple languages. We can add Hungarian and English.', '2026-03-22 13:00:00'),
(11, 44, 'Perfect. What about escalation to human agents?', '2026-03-22 14:00:00'),
(11, 94, 'We\'ll implement sentiment analysis to detect when to escalate.', '2026-03-22 15:00:00'),
(12, 45, 'Hi, for the healthcare portal, HIPAA compliance is crucial. How will you ensure it?', '2026-03-20 10:00:00'),
(12, 95, 'We\'ll use encryption, secure authentication, and regular security audits. All data will be encrypted at rest and in transit.', '2026-03-20 11:00:00'),
(12, 45, 'Good. What telemedicine features will be included?', '2026-03-20 12:00:00'),
(12, 95, 'Video calls, appointment scheduling, and secure messaging with doctors.', '2026-03-20 13:00:00'),
(12, 45, 'Excellent. When can we review the security protocols?', '2026-03-20 14:00:00'),
(12, 95, 'Next week. I\'ll prepare the documentation.', '2026-03-20 15:00:00'),
(13, 46, 'Hello, for the supply chain platform, what real-time tracking features will you implement?', '2026-03-19 10:00:00'),
(13, 96, 'GPS tracking, ETA predictions, and automated alerts for delays. Integration with IoT sensors.', '2026-03-19 11:00:00'),
(13, 46, 'Great. How about vendor performance analytics?', '2026-03-19 12:00:00'),
(13, 96, 'Dashboards with KPIs, delivery times, and quality metrics.', '2026-03-19 13:00:00'),
(13, 46, 'Perfect. What data sources will you need?', '2026-03-19 14:00:00'),
(13, 96, 'Shipment data, vendor information, and historical performance.', '2026-03-19 15:00:00'),
(14, 47, 'Hi, for the educational video platform, what adaptive bitrate streaming will you use?', '2026-03-23 10:00:00'),
(14, 97, 'We\'ll use HLS or DASH for adaptive streaming. Supports HD and 4K.', '2026-03-23 11:00:00'),
(14, 47, 'Good. How about live class integration?', '2026-03-23 12:00:00'),
(14, 97, 'Real-time streaming with chat and Q&A features.', '2026-03-23 13:00:00'),
(14, 47, 'Excellent. What about certificate generation?', '2026-03-23 14:00:00'),
(14, 97, 'Automated certificates upon course completion.', '2026-03-23 15:00:00'),
(15, 48, 'Hello, for the virtual tour platform, what 3D technologies will you use?', '2026-03-18 10:00:00'),
(15, 98, 'Three.js or Babylon.js for 3D rendering. Supports panoramic photos and floor plans.', '2026-03-18 11:00:00'),
(15, 48, 'Great. How about agent booking integration?', '2026-03-18 12:00:00'),
(15, 98, 'Direct booking forms with calendar integration.', '2026-03-18 13:00:00'),
(15, 48, 'Perfect. What SEO features?', '2026-03-18 14:00:00'),
(15, 98, 'Meta tags, sitemaps, and structured data for properties.', '2026-03-18 15:00:00'),
(16, 49, 'Hi, for the banking app, security is paramount. What measures will you implement?', '2026-03-17 10:00:00'),
(16, 99, 'Biometric authentication, end-to-end encryption, and regular penetration testing.', '2026-03-17 11:00:00'),
(16, 49, 'Good. What fintech APIs will be integrated?', '2026-03-17 12:00:00'),
(16, 99, 'Payment APIs, investment platforms, and budgeting tools.', '2026-03-17 13:00:00'),
(16, 49, 'Excellent. When can we discuss compliance?', '2026-03-17 14:00:00'),
(16, 99, 'Next Monday. I\'ll prepare the compliance checklist.', '2026-03-17 15:00:00'),
(17, 50, 'Hello, for the social analytics dashboard, what social platforms will you support?', '2026-03-16 10:00:00'),
(17, 100, 'Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn, and TikTok initially.', '2026-03-16 11:00:00'),
(17, 50, 'Great. How about real-time data processing?', '2026-03-16 12:00:00'),
(17, 100, 'Using streaming APIs and real-time databases.', '2026-03-16 13:00:00'),
(17, 50, 'Perfect. What reporting features?', '2026-03-16 14:00:00'),
(17, 100, 'Automated reports, custom dashboards, and trend analysis.', '2026-03-16 15:00:00'),
(18, 51, 'Hi, for the IoT building system, what protocols will you use?', '2026-03-15 10:00:00'),
(18, 101, 'MQTT and CoAP for IoT communication. Supports thousands of devices.', '2026-03-15 11:00:00'),
(18, 51, 'Good. How about predictive maintenance?', '2026-03-15 12:00:00'),
(18, 101, 'Machine learning algorithms to predict failures.', '2026-03-15 13:00:00'),
(18, 51, 'Excellent. What integration with existing systems?', '2026-03-15 14:00:00'),
(18, 101, 'APIs for HVAC, lighting, and security systems.', '2026-03-15 15:00:00'),
(19, 52, 'Hello, for the LMS, what adaptive learning features will you include?', '2026-03-14 10:00:00'),
(19, 102, 'Personalized learning paths based on student performance.', '2026-03-14 11:00:00'),
(19, 52, 'Great. How about offline learning?', '2026-03-14 12:00:00'),
(19, 102, 'Progressive Web App with offline capabilities.', '2026-03-14 13:00:00'),
(19, 52, 'Perfect. What assessment types?', '2026-03-14 14:00:00'),
(19, 102, 'Quizzes, assignments, and peer reviews.', '2026-03-14 15:00:00'),
(20, 53, 'Hi, for the blockchain supply chain, what consensus mechanism?', '2026-03-13 10:00:00'),
(20, 103, 'Proof of Work or Proof of Stake, depending on requirements.', '2026-03-13 11:00:00'),
(20, 53, 'Good. How about QR code integration?', '2026-03-13 12:00:00'),
(20, 103, 'For product verification and consumer tracking.', '2026-03-13 13:00:00'),
(20, 53, 'Excellent. What audit trails?', '2026-03-13 14:00:00'),
(20, 103, 'Immutable records of all transactions.', '2026-03-13 15:00:00'),
(21, 54, 'Hello, for the job matching platform, what ML algorithms?', '2026-03-12 10:00:00'),
(21, 104, 'Collaborative filtering and natural language processing.', '2026-03-12 11:00:00'),
(21, 54, 'Great. How about video interviews?', '2026-03-12 12:00:00'),
(21, 104, 'Integrated video platform with analysis.', '2026-03-12 13:00:00'),
(21, 54, 'Perfect. What data privacy measures?', '2026-03-12 14:00:00'),
(21, 104, 'GDPR compliance and data anonymization.', '2026-03-12 15:00:00'),
(22, 55, 'Hi, for the AR furniture app, what AR frameworks?', '2026-03-11 10:00:00'),
